A weathered stone tablet standing on a rocky cliff edge overlooking a stormy digital ocean, carved with exactly ten deep grooves representing commandments, each groove glowing with different neon cyberpunk colors - electric blue, hot pink, toxic green. The tablet is partially wrapped in thick chains and medieval locks, while streams of binary code rain down from dark purple storm clouds above. Circuit board patterns are etched into the stone's surface, merging ancient and futuristic aesthetics. Holographic shields and firewalls shimmer around the tablet like protective barriers. The ocean below churns with shadowy tentacle-like forms representing threats trying to reach the shore. Dramatic lighting from lightning strikes illuminates the scene with cyan and magenta hues.
